snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3006 - Abdul Missing?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Comedy | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा
snippet.description:

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:

Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

Gurucharan Singh as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3005 - Gokuldham Mein Corona?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi

Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3004 - Abdul बीमार | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा Comedy
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

snippet.title: BABY POTATO FRY | Roasted Potato fry Recipe Cooking in Village | Vegetarian Recipe | Potato Recipes
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook roasted potato fry recipe with 40 KG Baby Potatoes. We made special Chettinad masala by frying and grinding spices. 

We just add fried potatoes and fried masalas together to make potato fry.

Finally, we enjoy the fried potatoes with sambar.!

Ye video mein waise 5 scene the lekin 3 itne bade aur faad bane socha itna kaafi hai

snippet.title: Clash Royale: NEW CARD REVEAL ⚡ ELECTRO GIANT
snippet.description:
We welcome our 100th card to the Arena for the new SHOCKTOBER Season! 

... and our 101st as well. Why not. 😉

Play with ELECTRO GIANT this Shocktober starting October 5th!

Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale

Enter the Arena! From the creators of Clash of Clans comes a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash characters and much, much more.

Collect and upgrade dozens of cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defenses you know and love, as well as the Royales: Princes, Knights, Baby Dragons and more. Knock the enemy King and Princesses from their towers to defeat your opponents and win Trophies, Crowns and glory in the Arena. Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community.

Lead the Clash Royale Family to victory!

FEATURES
• Duel players from around the world in real-time in both 1v1 and 2v2 Battles
• Earn chests to unlock rewards, collect powerful new cards and upgrade existing ones
• Destroy opponent's towers and win Crowns to earn epic Crown chests
• Build and upgrade your card collection with the Clash Royale Family along with dozens of your favorite Clash troops, spells and defenses
• Construct your ultimate Battle Deck to defeat your opponents
• Progress through multiple Arenas all the way to the top
• Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community
• Challenge your Clanmates and friends to a private duel, or play side-by-side in a 2v2 Battle
• Work together with your Clan to unlock Clan Chests
• Play new events every week
• Learn different battle tactics by watching the best duels on TV Royale

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent's Guide:
http://supercell.com/en/parents/

#ClashRoyale #ElectroGiant #Shocktober

snippet.title: BLACKPINK – ‘Lovesick Girls’ M/V
snippet.description:
BLACKPINK – ‘Lovesick Girls’

영원한 밤
창문 없는 방에 우릴 가둔 love
What can we say
매번 아파도 외치는 love

다치고 망가져도 나
뭘 믿고 버티는 거야
어차피 떠나면 상처투성인 채로 미워하게 될걸
끝장을 보기 전 끝낼 순 없어
이 아픔을 기다린 것처럼

아마 다 잠깐 일지도 몰라
우린 무얼 찾아서 헤매는 걸까

But I don’t care I’ll do it over and over
내 세상 속엔 너만 있으면 돼

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔 없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

But we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone 
But why we still looking for love

No love letters, no x and o’s
No love never, my exes know
No diamond rings, that set in stone
To the left, better left alone

Didn’t wanna be a princess, I’m priceless
A prince not even on my list
Love is a drug that I quit
No doctor could help when I’m lovesick

아마 다 잠깐 일지도 몰라
우린 무얼 찾아서 헤매는 걸까

불안한 내 눈빛 속에 널 담아
아프더라도 너만 있으면 돼

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼 순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔 없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

But we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone 
But why we still looking for love

사랑은 slippin’ and fallin’
사랑은 killin’ your darlin’
아프다 아물면 또 찾아오는 이 겁 없는 떨림

들리지 않아 what you say
이 아픔이 난 행복해
나를 불쌍해 하는 네가 내 눈엔 더 불쌍해

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼 순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

Lovesick girls 
모두 결국 떠나가고
Lovesick girls
내 눈물이 무뎌져도
Lovesick girls
아프고 또 아파도
Lovesick girls
But we’re still looking for love

I wonder
if I’m being real do I speak my truth or do I filter to how I feel

What it’s like to be my friends
Hope that they don’t think I forget about them
I wonder
I wonder
 
Right before I close my eyes
The only thing that’s on my mind

I wonder

snippet.title: Clash Royale: NEW CARD REVEAL ⚡ ELECTRO GIANT
snippet.description:
We welcome our 100th card to the Arena for the new SHOCKTOBER Season! 

... and our 101st as well. Why not. 😉

Play with ELECTRO GIANT this Shocktober starting October 5th!

Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale

Enter the Arena! From the creators of Clash of Clans comes a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash characters and much, much more.

Collect and upgrade dozens of cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defenses you know and love, as well as the Royales: Princes, Knights, Baby Dragons and more. Knock the enemy King and Princesses from their towers to defeat your opponents and win Trophies, Crowns and glory in the Arena. Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community.

Lead the Clash Royale Family to victory!

FEATURES
• Duel players from around the world in real-time in both 1v1 and 2v2 Battles
• Earn chests to unlock rewards, collect powerful new cards and upgrade existing ones
• Destroy opponent's towers and win Crowns to earn epic Crown chests
• Build and upgrade your card collection with the Clash Royale Family along with dozens of your favorite Clash troops, spells and defenses
• Construct your ultimate Battle Deck to defeat your opponents
• Progress through multiple Arenas all the way to the top
• Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community
• Challenge your Clanmates and friends to a private duel, or play side-by-side in a 2v2 Battle
• Work together with your Clan to unlock Clan Chests
• Play new events every week
• Learn different battle tactics by watching the best duels on TV Royale

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent's Guide:
http://supercell.com/en/parents/

#ClashRoyale #ElectroGiant #Shocktober

snippet.title: The Witches - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Witches are real, and they are everywhere! 🐀 Watch the official trailer for #TheWitchesHBOMax streaming exclusively on HBOMax in the US on October 22! 

From Oscar-winning director Robert Zemeckis (“Forrest Gump”) comes the fantasy adventure “Roald Dahl’s The Witches.”  The film stars Oscar winners Anne Hathaway (“Les Misérable,” “Ocean’s 8”) and Octavia Spencer (“The Help,” “The Shape of Water”), Oscar nominee Stanley Tucci (“The Hunger Games” films, “The Lovely Bones”), with Kristin Chenoweth (TV’s “Glee” and “BoJack Horseman”) and award-winning comedy legend Chris Rock.  Newcomer Jahzir Kadeem Bruno (TV’s “Atlanta”) also stars, alongside Codie-Lei Eastick (“Holmes & Watson”).

Reimagining Dahl’s beloved story for a modern audience, Zemeckis’s visually innovative film tells the darkly humorous and heartwarming tale of a young orphaned boy (Bruno) who, in late 1967, goes to live with his loving Grandma (Spencer) in the rural Alabama town of Demopolis.  As the boy and his grandmother encounter some deceptively glamorous but thoroughly diabolical witches, she wisely whisks our young hero away to an opulent seaside resort.  Regrettably, they arrive at precisely the same time that the world’s Grand High Witch (Hathaway) has gathered her fellow cronies from around the globe—undercover—to carry out her nefarious plans.

Based on the book by Roald Dahl, the screenplay is by Robert Zemeckis & Kenya Barris (TV’s “black-ish,” “Shaft”) and Oscar winner Guillermo del Toro (“The Shape of Water”).  Zemeckis is also producing, alongside Jack Rapke, del Toro, Alfonso Cuarón and Luke Kelly.  Serving as executive producers are Jacqueline Levine, Marianne Jenkins, Michael Siegel, Gideon Simeloff and Cate Adams.

Zemeckis’s behind-the-scenes team includes a roster of his frequent collaborators, including Oscar-nominated director of photography Don Burgess (“Forrest Gump”), production designer Gary Freeman, editors Jeremiah O’Driscoll and Ryan Chan, Oscar-nominated costume designer Joanna Johnston (“Allied,” “Lincoln”), and Oscar-nominated composer Alan Silvestri (“Polar Express,” “Forrest Gump”).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents, an Image Movers/Necropia/Experanto Filmoj Production, a Robert Zemeckis Film, “Roald Dahl’s The Witches.”  
TheWitchesMovie.com

Witches are real, and they are everywhere! 🐀 Watch the official trailer for #TheWitchesHBOMax streaming exclusively on HBOMax in the US on October 22! 

From Oscar-winning director Robert Zemeckis (“Forrest Gump”) comes the fantasy adventure “Roald Dahl’s The Witches.”  The film stars Oscar winners Anne Hathaway (“Les Misérable,” “Ocean’s 8”) and Octavia Spencer (“The Help,” “The Shape of Water”), Oscar nominee Stanley Tucci (“The Hunger Games” films, “The Lovely Bones”), with Kristin Chenoweth (TV’s “Glee” and “BoJack Horseman”) and award-winning comedy legend Chris Rock.  Newcomer Jahzir Kadeem Bruno (TV’s “Atlanta”) also stars, alongside Codie-Lei Eastick (“Holmes & Watson”).

Reimagining Dahl’s beloved story for a modern audience, Zemeckis’s visually innovative film tells the darkly humorous and heartwarming tale of a young orphaned boy (Bruno) who, in late 1967, goes to live with his loving Grandma (Spencer) in the rural Alabama town of Demopolis.  As the boy and his grandmother encounter some deceptively glamorous but thoroughly diabolical witches, she wisely whisks our young hero away to an opulent seaside resort.  Regrettably, they arrive at precisely the same time that the world’s Grand High Witch (Hathaway) has gathered her fellow cronies from around the globe—undercover—to carry out her nefarious plans.

Based on the book by Roald Dahl, the screenplay is by Robert Zemeckis & Kenya Barris (TV’s “black-ish,” “Shaft”) and Oscar winner Guillermo del Toro (“The Shape of Water”).  Zemeckis is also producing, alongside Jack Rapke, del Toro, Alfonso Cuarón and Luke Kelly.  Serving as executive producers are Jacqueline Levine, Marianne Jenkins, Michael Siegel, Gideon Simeloff and Cate Adams.

Zemeckis’s behind-the-scenes team includes a roster of his frequent collaborators, including Oscar-nominated director of photography Don Burgess (“Forrest Gump”), production designer Gary Freeman, editors Jeremiah O’Driscoll and Ryan Chan, Oscar-nominated costume designer Joanna Johnston (“Allied,” “Lincoln”), and Oscar-nominated composer Alan Silvestri (“Polar Express,” “Forrest Gump”).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents, an Image Movers/Necropia/Experanto Filmoj Production, a Robert Zemeckis Film, “Roald Dahl’s The Witches.”  
TheWitchesMovie.com

snippet.title: Northrop Grumman Cargo Launch to the Space Station from NASA Wallops
snippet.description: Tune in to watch live as Northrop Grumman launches its Antares rocket and Cygnus spacecraft on a resupply mission to the International Space Station. Liftoff is now targeted for 9:16 p.m. EDT from NASA's Wallops Flight Facility in Virginia. A previous launch attempt on Oct. 1 was scrubbed. Payloads on board Cygnus include research to help identify targeted cancer therapies, a new space toilet, a crop of radishes that will grow in the station's advanced plant habitat, a virtual reality camera that will capture a future spacewalk, and more.

snippet.title: HEAT at LAKERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | October 2, 2020
snippet.description:
HEAT at LAKERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | October 2, 2020

Led by LeBron James’ 33 PTS, 9 REB and 9 AST, the Los Angeles Lakers defeated the Miami Heat, 124-114. Additionally for the Lakers, Anthony Davis recorded 32 PTS and 14 REB in the victory, while Jimmy Butler tallied 25 PTS, 8 REB and a playoff career-high 13 AST for the Heat.

The Lakers lead this best-of-seven series, 2-0. Game 3 will take place on Sunday, October 4 at 7:30pm/et on ABC!

snippet.description:

The 74-year-old said the couple were self-isolating after Hope Hicks, one of his top aides, tested positive.

His health records showed he is categorised as obese, putting him at higher risk of serious complications from the virus.

snippet.title: Apex Legends Aftermarket Collection Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Dive into cross-play beta, take on the “Flashpoint” limited-time mode, and unlock up to 24 Event-Limited items! Learn More 

Cross-play beta is here, along with the Aftermarket Collection Event. In the new “Flashpoint” LTM there are no shield or health pickups. Instead, you'll regain health in Flashpoint zones. Just don’t stay too long, there will be plenty of other squads closing in fast. Take on challenges to earn exclusive rewards, and visit the store to unlock up to 24 Event-Limited items. Get the entire collection to call yourself a champ and unlock the new Caustic Heirloom. It’s going to be a hell of a ride!

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC. 

Learn more about Apex Legends Season 6 – Boosted: http://x.ea.com/64060
 
Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

#Crossplay #PlayApex #ApexSeason6 #AftermarketEvent #ApexLegends

localizations.ko.title: Apex 레전드 애프터마켓 수집품 이벤트 트레일러
localizations.ko.description:
크로스플레이에 뛰어들고, ""플래시포인트"" 기간 한정 모드에 참가하세요. 24종의 이벤트 한정 아이템을 획득하세요! 자세히 보기 


크로스플레이와 애프터마켓 수집품 이벤트가 시작되었습니다. 새로운 ""플래시포인트"" 기간 한정 모드에선 실드나 회복 아이템이 없습니다. 대신 플래시포인트 존에서 체력을 회복할 수 있습니다. 너무 오래 머무르진 마세요. 빠르게 다가오는 다른 분대가 많을 것입니다. 챌린지를 완수하여 한정판 보상을 획득하고 스토어에 방문하여 최대 24종의 이벤트 한정 아이템을 획득하세요. 수집품을 완성하여 멋진 챔피언이 되고 새로운 코스틱 영웅 치장 아이템을 잠금 해제하세요. 스릴 넘치는 경기가 기다리고 있습니다! 

Apex 레전드™는 전설적인 캐릭터들이 영광과 명성, 부를 쟁취하기 위해 프런티어의 변경에서 치열한 전투를 벌이는 부분 유료 배틀 로얄 게임입니다. Xbox One, PlayStation 4 및 PC용 Origin에서 Apex 레전드를 무료 플레이하십시오. 

Apex 레전드 시즌 6 – 부스티드의 더 자세한 정보: http://x.ea.com/ko-kr/64060

localizations.ru.title: Apex Legends — трейлер коллекционного события «Переоборудование»
localizations.ru.description:
Начните кроссплатформенную игру, покорите временный режим «Очаг опасности» и откройте до 24 предметов, доступных во время события! Узнайте подробности


Встречайте кроссплатформенную игру и коллекционное событие «Переоборудование». В новом временном режиме «Очаг опасности» вы не найдете среди добычи щитов или предметов лечения. Вместо этого здоровье восстанавливается в зонах очагов. Только не задерживайтесь, очень скоро туда заявятся и другие отряды. Проходите испытания с эксклюзивными наградами и наведайтесь в магазин, чтобы открыть до 24 предметов, доступных во время события. Собрав полную коллекцию, достойную чемпиона, вы откроете новую реликвию Каустика. Будет жарко! 

Apex Legends™ — бесплатная игра в жанре «королевская битва», где легендарные персонажи сражаются за славу и богатства на дальних рубежах Фронтира. Играйте бесплатно на Xbox One, PS4 и в Origin для ПК. 

Узнайте больше о сезоне 6 Apex Legends «Разгон»: http://x.ea.com/64060
 
Загляните на наш канал на YouTube: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Следите за нашей страницей в Twitter: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Подпишитесь на нашу страницу в Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

#Crossplay #PlayApex #ApexSeason6 #AftermarketEvent #ApexLegends
localizations.cs.title: Upoutávka na sběratelskou herní událost Aftermarket v Apex Legends
localizations.cs.description:
Vyzkoušejte hraní napříč platformami, zahrajte si časově omezený režim „Flashpoint“ a odemkněte až 24 předmětů dostupných v rámci herní události! Více informací 


Přichází hraní napříč platformami spolu se sběratelskou herní událostí Aftermarket. V novém, časově omezeném režimu „Flashpoint“ nenajdete předměty štítů ani zdraví. Místo toho si zdraví obnovujete v zónách Flashpoint. Jen tam moc dlouho nestůjte, protože o ně bude jistě velký zájem ze strany ostatních týmů. Dokončením výzev získejte exkluzivní odměny a v obchodě si odemkněte až 24 předmětů dostupných pouze po dobu herní události. Zkompletujte sbírku, ať se můžete nazývat šampiony, a odemkněte nový Caustic Heirloom. Bude to pořádná jízda! 

Apex Legends™ je bezplatná (F2P) hra žánru battle royale, v níž legendární postavy bojují v okrajových částech Pohraničí o slávu a bohatství. Zahrajte si zdarma ještě dnes na Xboxu One, PS4 a PC (Origin). 

Více informací o 6. sezóně Apex Legends s názvem Boosted: http://x.ea.com/64060
 
Podívejte se na náš kanál na YouTube: http://x.ea.com/56710.

localizations.ja.title: 「エーペックスレジェンズ」アフターマーケット コレクションイベント トレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
クロスプレイを導入した期間限定モード,「フラッシュポイント」に挑戦。24種類のイベント限定アイテムを手に入れよう！詳細をチェック


アフターマーケット コレクションイベントの開催に合わせて,クロスプレイも新登場。期間限定モードの「フラッシュポイント」では,シールドや体力回復アイテムがマップから消滅してしまう。その代わりに,フラッシュポイントゾーンで体力が回復するシステムになっている。ここには我先にと多くの部隊が集結することが予想される。長居は禁物だ。チャレンジをクリアすれば限定報酬を獲得でき,ストアには最大24種類のイベント限定アイテムも用意されている。コレクションを完了し,その偉業にふさわしい新登場のコースティックのスーパーレジェンドアイテムを目指せ。最高の体験と最高のアイテムが君を待っている！

「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は,伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う,基本プレイ無料のバトルロイヤル作品。Xbox One,PS4,Origin（PC）で今すぐ無料プレイ。

「エーペックスレジェンズ シーズン6 – ブーステッド」の詳細はこちらでチェック：http://x.ea.com/64060

localizations.es-ES.title: Tráiler del evento de colección Mercado de repuestos de Apex Legends
localizations.es-ES.description:
¡Sumérgete enel crossplay, enfréntate al modo por tiempo limitado Punto de conflicto y desbloquea hasta 24 objetos limitados del evento! Más información 


Ya ha llegado el crossplay, junto con el evento de colección Mercado de repuestos. En el nuevo modo por tiempo limitado Punto de conflicto no hay kits de salud ni escudos. En su lugar, recuperarás la salud en las zonas de Punto de conflicto. Pero no permanezcas en ellas mucho tiempo: numerosos pelotones te pisarán los talones. Completa retos para obtener recompensas exclusivas y visita la tienda para desbloquear hasta 24 objetos limitados del evento. Completa la colección como todo un campeón y desbloquea la nueva reliquia de Caustic. ¡La cosa va a estar movidita! 

Apex Legends™ es un juego de Battle Royale gratuito donde personajes legendarios se enfrentan para lograr gloria, fama y fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega ya gratis en Xbox One, PS4 y Origin para PC. 

Obtén más información sobre la temporada 6 de Apex Legends: A tope en http://x.ea.com/64060

localizations.zh-Hant.title: 《Apex 英雄》零件市場收藏活動預告片
localizations.zh-Hant.description:
加入跨平台遊戲,挑戰「閃燃點」限時模式,並解鎖高達 24 款活動限定道具！瞭解詳情


跨平台遊戲與零件市場收藏活動已經登場。在全新的「閃燃點」限時模式中,無法取得防護罩或治療道具,取而代之的是在閃燃點區中恢復生命值。不過可別待太久了,還有許多隊伍將蜂擁而至。完成挑戰以獲得獨家獎勵,造訪商店來解鎖多達 24 款活動限定道具。完成收藏並自封為王,同時解鎖全新的腐蝕傳家寶。這下可精彩了！

《Apex 英雄》是一款免費遊玩的戰術競技遊戲,其中的挑戰者來自邊境各處並為了榮耀,名聲與財富而戰。立即在 Xbox One,PS4 與 PC Origin 上免費遊玩。

深入瞭解《Apex 英雄》賽季 6 - 勢不可擋：http://x.ea.com/64060

localizations.it.title: Evento collezione Aftermarket - Il trailer
localizations.it.description:
Immergiti nel Cross-Play, scopri la modalità a tempo limitato Flashpoint e sblocca fino a 24 oggetti evento! Scopri di più 


Il Cross-Play è finalmente arrivato, insieme all'evento collezione Aftermarket. Nella nuova modalità a tempo limitato Flashpoint, gli oggetti di cura e gli scudi sono stati rimossi. In compenso potrai rigenerare la salute in aree specifiche. Ma non fermarti troppo a lungo, perché le altre squadre arriveranno in fretta! Ottieni ricompense esclusive completando le sfide e visita il negozio per sbloccare fino a 24 oggetti evento limitati. Completa la collezione e dimostra di essere una vera leggenda per ricevere il nuovo Set cimelio di famiglia di Caustic. Sarà un'avventura indimenticabile! 

Apex Legends™ è un gioco gratuito in stile battle royale in cui personaggi leggendari si sfidano per gloria, fama e ricchezza ai margini della Frontiera. Gioca gratis su Xbox One, PlayStation 4 e Origin per PC. 

Scopri di più su Massima potenza, la sesta stagione di Apex Legends: http://x.ea.com/64060

localizations.fi.title: Apex Legends Aftermarket Collection -tapahtuman traileri
localizations.fi.description:
Hyppää cross-playhin, koe rajoitetun ajan Flashpoint-pelitila ja avaa jopa 24 tapahtumaan rajoitettua esinettä! Lue lisää 
 
 
 Cross-play on täällä – osallistu Aftermarket Collection-tapahtumaan. Uudessa rajoitetun ajan pelitilassa Flashpointissa ei ole shield- eikä terveysesineitä. Terveyttä on sen sijaan palautettava Flashpoint Zoneissa. Älä kuitenkaan pysy niissä liian kauaa, sillä muut tiimit lähestyvät. Suorita haasteita ja voita eksklusiivisia palkintoja – käy kaupassa avaamassa käyttöösi jopa 24 tapahtumaan rajoitettua esinettä. Täydennä kokoelma, niin voit kutsua itseäsi mestariksi ja saat uuden Caustic Heirloomin. Tästä tulee rankka reissu! 
 
 Apex Legends™ on ilmainen battle royale -peli, jossa legendaariset hahmot taistelevat maineesta, kunniasta ja mammonasta Frontierin laitamilla. Pelaa nyt ilmaiseksi Xbox Onella, PS4-järjestelmällä ja PC:llä Originin kautta. 
 
 Lue lisää Apex Legends Season 6 – Boostedista: http://x.ea.com/64060
 
 Tsekkaa YouTube-kanavamme: http://x.ea.com/56710.
 Seuraa meitä Twitterissä: https://twitter.com/playapex.
 Seuraa meitä Instagramissa: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.
 
 #Crossplay #PlayApex #ApexSeason6 #AftermarketEvent #ApexLegends
localizations.de-DE.title: Apex Legends – Zubehörmarkt-Sammel-Event-Trailer
localizations.de-DE.description:
Stürze dich in das Crossplay, spiele den befristeten Flashpoint-Modus und schalte bis zu 24 Event-exklusive Objekte frei! Mehr erfahren. 


Crossplay und das Zubehörmarkt-Sammel-Event sind da! Im neuen befristeten Flashpoint-Modus gibt es keine Schilde oder Gesundheit-Pickups. Stattdessen regenerierst du Gesundheit in Flashpoint-Zonen. Bleib nur nicht zu lange, weil sich jede Menge andere Squads rasch nähern. Schließe Herausforderungen ab, um exklusive Belohnungen zu erhalten, und besucht den Store, um bis zu 24 Event-exklusive Objekte freizuschalten. Vervollständige die Sammlung, um dich selbst zum Champ zu krönen und das neue Caustic-Erbstück freizuschalten. Das wird ein echter Höllenritt. 

Apex Legends™ ist ein Free-to-Play-Battle-Royale-Spiel, bei dem legendäre Charaktere am Rande des Grenzlands um Ruhm und Reichtum kämpfen. Jetzt kostenlos auf Xbox One, PS4 und Origin für PC spielen. 

Erfahre mehr über Apex Legends Saison 6 – Maximale Leistung: http://x.ea.com/64060
 
Besuche unseren YouTube-Kanal: http://x.ea.com/56710.

localizations.pt-PT.title: Apex Legends – Trailer do Evento de Coleção Aftermarket
localizations.pt-PT.description:
Participa no cross-play, experimenta o modo temporário ""Flashpoint"" e desbloqueia até 24 itens limitados ao evento! Mais informações 


Chegou o cross-play, e com ele chega também o Evento de Coleção Aftermarket. Não há escudos nem recolhas de vida no evento temporário ""Flashpoint"". Em vez disso, recuperas vida nas zonas Flashpoint. Mas não fiques lá muito tempo, pois os outros esquadrões farão o mesmo. Conclui desafios para obter recompensas exclusivas e visita a loja para desbloquear até 24 itens limitados ao evento. Completa a coleção, sobe ao pódio de campeão e desbloqueia a nova relíquia para Caustic. Vai ser uma aventura e tanto! 

Apex Legends™ é um jogo gratuito do género battle royale onde personagens lendárias lutam por glória, fama e fortuna nas periferias da Fronteira. Joga já de graça na Xbox One, PS4 e Origin para PC.

localizations.pl.title: Apex Legends – zwiastun wydarzenia „Rynek wtórny”
localizations.pl.description:
Wypróbuj grę międzyplatformową, zmierz się z ograniczonym czasowo trybem Punkt krytyczny i odblokuj nawet 24 przedmioty z wydarzenia! Dowiedz się więcej 


Gra międzyplatformowa jest już dostępna, a wraz z nią do Apex Legends trafia wydarzenie „Rynek wtórny”. W nowym, ograniczonym czasowo trybie Punkt krytyczny, gracze nie mogą korzystać z tarcz ani przedmiotów uzdrawiających. Jedynym sposobem na przywrócenie zdrowia jest przebywanie w specjalnych strefach punktów krytycznych. Pamiętaj tylko, by nie zostawać w nich zbyt długo – inne oddziały mogą się zjawić w każdej chwili. Wykonuj wyzwania, by zdobyć wyjątkowe nagrody i odwiedzaj sklep, by odblokować nawet 24 przedmioty z wydarzenia. Zbierz całą kolekcję, aby zasłużyć na tytuł czempiona i odblokować nową pamiątkę Caustica. Czeka was niezła jazda! 

Apex Legends™ to darmowa gra Battle Royale, w której legendarne postacie mierzą się ze sobą w walce o sławę i chwałę na obrzeżach Kresów. Graj w Apex Legends za darmo już teraz – na Xbox One, PlayStation 4 oraz Origin na PC. 

Dowiedz się więcej o sezonie 6. Apex Legends – Dopalacz: http://x.ea.com/64060

localizations.zh-Hans.description:
加入跨平台游戏,挑战“闪点”限时模式,并解锁多达 24 件活动限定物品！了解详情


跨平台游戏和零件市场收集活动已经登场。在新的“闪点”限时模式中,无法取得护盾或治疗物品,取而代之的是,能在闪点区域内恢复生命值。不过可别待太久,还有很多队伍正蜂拥而至。完成挑战,赢取专属奖励,逛逛商店,解锁多达 24 件活动限定物品集齐收藏品,成为捍卫者,解锁全新侵蚀传家宝。这将是一段劲爆的旅程！

《Apex Legends™》是一款免费游玩的战术竞技游戏,其中的挑战者来自边境各地并为了荣耀,名声与财富而战。赶快在 Xbox One,PS4 和 PC 端 Origin 上免费游玩。

localizations.nl-NL.title: Apex Legends Aftermarket Collection Event-trailer
localizations.nl-NL.description:
Stort je in cross-play, speel de tijdelijke modus “Flashpoint” en krijg toegang tot maximaal 24 exclusieve evenement-items! Meer info 


Cross-play is aangekomen, samen met het Aftermarket Collection Event. In de nieuwe “Flashpoint” LTM zijn er geen schild- of energie-pickups. In plaats daarvan krijg je energie in Flashpoint-zones. Blijf er alleen niet te lang, want er komen al snel talloze andere squads aan. Voltooi uitdagingen om exclusieve beloningen te verdienen en bezoek de store om maximaal 24 exclusieve evenement-items vrij te spelen. Maak de collectie compleet om jezelf kampioen te noemen en toegang te krijgen tot het nieuwe Caustic Heirloom. Het wordt een geweldige rit! 

Apex Legends™ is een free-to-play battle royale-spel waarin legendarische personages strijden om glorie, roem en fortuin aan de rand van de Frontier. Speel nu gratis op de Xbox One, PS4 en Origin for PC.

localizations.sv.title: Apex Legends trailer för samlarevenemanget Aftermarket
localizations.sv.description:
Kasta dig in i crossplay, ta dig an det tisdbegränsade läget “Flashpoint” och lås upp fram till 24 evenemangsbegränsade föremål! Läs mer 


Crossplay är här tillsammans med samlarevenemanget Aftermarket. I det nya tidsbegränsade läget “Flashpoint” finns det inga sköld- eller hälsoupphämtningar. Istället återfår du hälsa i Flashpoint-zoner. Stanna bara inte för länge, många trupper kommer att närma sig snabbt. Klara av utmaningar för att få exklusiva föremål och gå till butiken där upp till 24 evenemangsbegränsade föremål finns att låsa upp. Slutför samlingen för att kalla dig själv mästare och lås upp nya Caustic Heirloom. Det blir en jäklans åktur! 

Apex Legends™ är ett gratis battle royale-spel där legendariska karaktärer strider för ära, berömmelse och rikedom på gränslandets utkanter. Spela gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4 och Origin för PC.

localizations.es-MX.title: Tráiler del evento de colección Mercado de repuestos de Apex Legends
localizations.es-MX.description:
¡Descubre el Cross-Play, enfréntate al modo Punto de conflicto por tiempo limitado y desbloquea hasta 24 artículos limitados del evento! Más información 


El Cross-Play llegó con el evento de colección Mercado de repuestos. En el nuevo modo Punto de conflicto por tiempo limitado no se pueden recoger escudos ni salud. En su lugar, recuperarás salud en las zonas de Punto de conflicto. Pero no estés demasiado tiempo, porque el resto de escuadrones también irán allí. Completa desafíos para ganar recompensas exclusivas y visita la Tienda para desbloquear hasta 24 artículos limitados del evento. Completa la colección para coronarte campeón y desbloquear la nueva reliquia de Caustic. ¡Será toda una aventura! 

Apex Legends™ es un juego gratuito estilo Battle Royale en el que personajes legendarios luchan por la gloria, la fama y la fortuna en los límites de la Frontera. Juega gratis ahora en Xbox One, PS4™ y Origin para PC.

localizations.fr-FR.title: Apex Legends - Trailer de l’événement de collection Marché secondaire
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Découvrez le Cross-Play, participez au mode Point d’ignition à durée limitée et débloquez jusqu’à 24 objets d’événement ! En savoir plus 


Découvrez le Cross-Play avec l’événement de collection Marché secondaire. Dans le mode Point d’ignition à durée limitée, vous ne disposerez d’aucun bouclier ni kit de soins. Seules les zones de Point d’ignition vous permettront de vous soigner. Ne vous y attardez pas, car une multitude d’autres équipes chercheront aussi à s’y rendre ! Relevez des défis pour gagner du contenu exclusif et visitez la Boutique pour débloquer jusqu’à 24 objets limités à l’événement. Terminez l’événement de collection pour décrocher les honneurs et débloquer le set Héritage de Caustic. Cette nouvelle virée s’annonce mouvementée ! 

Apex Legends™ est un jeu de tir Battle Royale Free-to-Play où des personnages légendaires combattent ensemble aux confins de la Frontière pour la gloire et la fortune. Jouez gratuitement sur PlayStation 4, Xbox One et Origin pour PC.

localizations.no.title: Apex Legends Aftermarket-samlehendelse – trailer
localizations.no.description:
Opplev tverrspilling, prøv den tidsbegrensede modusen «Flashpoint» og lås opp opptil 24 hendelseseksklusive elementer. Mer informasjon 


Tverrspilling er på plass, sammen med «Aftermarket»-samlehendelsen. I den nye tidsbegrensede modusen «Flashpoint» er det ingen skjold eller gjenstander som fyller opp liv. Som et alternativ fyller du opp livet ditt i Flashpoint-soner. Men ikke bli værende i dem for lenge, for det er sikkert mange andre grupper på vei også. Fullfør utfordringer for å låse opp eksklusive belønninger og besøk butikken for å låse opp opptil 24 hendelseseksklusive elementer. Fullfør samlingen for å kalle deg selv en mester og lås opp Caustic sin nye heirloom. Det blir litt av en opplevelse! 

Apex Legends™ er et battle royale-spill som er gratis å spille, hvor legendariske karakterer kjemper om rikdom og ære i utkanten av grenselandet. Spill gratis på Xbox One, PS4 og Origin for PC nå. 

Mer informasjon om Apex Legends – Sesong 6 – Boosted: http://x.ea.com/64060

localizations.da.title: Apex Legends – Aftermarket Collection-begivenhedstrailer
localizations.da.description:
Kast dig ud i cross-play, prøv kræfter med den tidsbegrænsede spiltype ""Flashpoint"", og lås op for 24 genstande, der er begrænset til begivenheden! Få mere at vide 


Cross-play er her sammen med Aftermarket Collection-begivenheden. I den nye ""Flashpoint"" LTM er der ingen skjolde eller førstehjælpskasser, som kan samles op. I stedet skal du genoplade din energi i Flashpoint-zoner. Men pas på med at blive hængende for længe, for de andre hold vil også bruge zonerne. Gennemfør udfordringerne for at få eksklusive belønninger, og besøg butikken for at låse op for 24 genstande, der er begrænsede til begivenheden. Fuldend samlingen, så du kan kalde dig selv for mester, og lås op for det nye Caustic Heirloom. Det bliver for vildt! 

Apex Legends™ er et gratis Battle Royale-spil, hvor legendariske karakterer kæmper om hæder, berømmelse og held i grænseområdet. Spil gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4 og Origin til pc.

localizations.pt-BR.description:
Mergulhe no Crossplay, participe do modo de tempo limitado ""Ponto-quente"" e desbloqueie até 24 itens de evento limitados! Saiba mais 


O modo Crossplay chegou, junto ao Evento de Coleção Segunda Mão. No novo modo de tempo limitado ""Ponto-quente"", não há itens de escudo ou cura. Em vez disso, você recupera vida nas áreas de ""Ponto-quente"". Mas não fique lá por muito tempo, há vários esquadrões chegando. Conclua os desafios para ganhar recompensas exclusivas e visite a loja para desbloquear até 24 itens limitados do evento. Complete a coleção para ganhar o título de campeão e desbloquear a nova Herança do Caustic. Vai ser um desafio e tanto! 

Apex Legends™ é um jogo gratuito de battle royale em que personagens lendários lutam por glória, fama e fortuna nos limites da Fronteira. Jogue Apex Legends de graça agora no Xbox One, PlayStation®4 e Origin para PC.

snippet.title: EVERY DAY AMONG US LIFE ANIMATION 4# GREEN & PET
snippet.description:
A normal day in Among Us animation part 4!

Thanks you so much for support me! 
I love you! ❤️

Original Animation by Hornstromp.

Among Us is an American made science fiction based murder mystery video game developed and published by Innersloth. Inc. It was released for IOS and Android on June 15, 2018, for PC on Steam on August 18, 2018 and for Dajolg on November 2, 2018. Among Us follows a crew being picked off one by one by an impostor.

In each game the player is one of 4 to 10 living and working in several different environments. One of these crewmates is an Impostor whose main goal is to kill everyone else. The remainder of the players are part of the regular crew who are just trying to escape unharmed. To do this, they have to complete several tasks or (better yet) find the Impostor and vote them out Survivor-style. If they are successful, the Crew wins. snippet.title: The Infinite Pattern That Never Repeats
snippet.description:
Simples rules of geometry meant that 5-fold symmetry was impossible as were crystals without a periodic structure. This turns out to be wrong. Thanks to LastPass for sponsoring a portion of this video. Click here to start using LastPass: https://ve42.co/LPs

Huge thanks to Prof. Paul Steinhardt for the interview on this topic. Check out his book ‘The Second Kind of Impossible’

If you'd like to learn more about Penrose tilings, go check out "Penrose Tiles to Trapdoor Ciphers" by Martin Gardener, which helped my research for this video.

Filmed by Gene Nagata (Potato Jet on YouTube)
Animations by Iván Tello and Jonny Hyman
Editing, Coloring, Music & Audio mastering by Jonny Hyman

Prague scenes filmed in 2012.
Special thanks to Raquel Nuno for helping with the tilings!

Additional Music from Epidemic Sound

snippet.title: Everything Wrong With Jennifer's Body In 18 Minutes Or Less

Next week: Stop Motion sins and Space sins. 

Remember, no movie is without sin. Which movie's sins should we count next?

snippet.title: The Witches - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Witches are real, and they are everywhere! 🐀 Watch the official trailer for #TheWitchesHBOMax streaming exclusively on HBOMax in the US on October 22! 

From Oscar-winning director Robert Zemeckis (“Forrest Gump”) comes the fantasy adventure “Roald Dahl’s The Witches.”  The film stars Oscar winners Anne Hathaway (“Les Misérable,” “Ocean’s 8”) and Octavia Spencer (“The Help,” “The Shape of Water”), Oscar nominee Stanley Tucci (“The Hunger Games” films, “The Lovely Bones”), with Kristin Chenoweth (TV’s “Glee” and “BoJack Horseman”) and award-winning comedy legend Chris Rock.  Newcomer Jahzir Kadeem Bruno (TV’s “Atlanta”) also stars, alongside Codie-Lei Eastick (“Holmes & Watson”).

Reimagining Dahl’s beloved story for a modern audience, Zemeckis’s visually innovative film tells the darkly humorous and heartwarming tale of a young orphaned boy (Bruno) who, in late 1967, goes to live with his loving Grandma (Spencer) in the rural Alabama town of Demopolis.  As the boy and his grandmother encounter some deceptively glamorous but thoroughly diabolical witches, she wisely whisks our young hero away to an opulent seaside resort.  Regrettably, they arrive at precisely the same time that the world’s Grand High Witch (Hathaway) has gathered her fellow cronies from around the globe—undercover—to carry out her nefarious plans.

Based on the book by Roald Dahl, the screenplay is by Robert Zemeckis & Kenya Barris (TV’s “black-ish,” “Shaft”) and Oscar winner Guillermo del Toro (“The Shape of Water”).  Zemeckis is also producing, alongside Jack Rapke, del Toro, Alfonso Cuarón and Luke Kelly.  Serving as executive producers are Jacqueline Levine, Marianne Jenkins, Michael Siegel, Gideon Simeloff and Cate Adams.

Zemeckis’s behind-the-scenes team includes a roster of his frequent collaborators, including Oscar-nominated director of photography Don Burgess (“Forrest Gump”), production designer Gary Freeman, editors Jeremiah O’Driscoll and Ryan Chan, Oscar-nominated costume designer Joanna Johnston (“Allied,” “Lincoln”), and Oscar-nominated composer Alan Silvestri (“Polar Express,” “Forrest Gump”).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents, an Image Movers/Necropia/Experanto Filmoj Production, a Robert Zemeckis Film, “Roald Dahl’s The Witches.”  
TheWitchesMovie.com

snippet.title: Michael Gove Visits Mistress Priti Patel's Boudoir | Spitting Image
snippet.description:
From the very first episode of Spitting image, Michael Gove Visits Mistress Priti Patel's Boudoir for some kinky conservative opinions.

Watch Spitting Image Saturdays on BritBox.

Subscribe for more Spitting Image: http://bit.ly/SpittingImageSub 
Follow Spitting Image on Twitter: twitter.com/SpittingImage
Like Spitting Image on Facebook: facebook.com/SpittingImage
Follow Spitting Imgae on Instagram: instagram.com/SpittingImages 

With the world getting smaller and more turbulent, the time couldn’t be more appropriate for an iconic British satirical take on global events. Produced by Avalon (Taskmaster, The Russell Howard Hour, Catastrophe, Breeders, Last Week Tonight With John Oliver) throughout the COVID-19 pandemic, over 100 puppets have already been developed by socially distanced teams of artists ready for launch, including: Adele, Angela Merkel, Baby Yoda, Barack Obama, Beyoncé, Billie Eilish, Boris Johnson, Boris Baby, The Johnson Dog, Brad Pitt, Camilla Duchess of Cornwall, Covid-19, Cristiano Ronaldo, Dominic Cummings, Dominic Raab, Donald Trump, Dwayne Johnson, Ed Sheeran, Elon Musk, Elton John, Emmanuel Macron, Greta Thunberg, Grimes, Gwyneth Paltrow, Harry Styles, Idris Elba, Ivanka Trump, Jacinda Ardern, James Corden, Jeff Bezos, Joe Biden, Jürgen Klopp, Kanye West, Keir Starmer, Kim Kardashian, Lewis Hamilton, Mark Zuckerberg, Matt Hancock, Meghan Duchess of Sussex, Melania Trump, Michael Gove, Michelle Obama, Narendra Modi, Oprah Winfrey, Piers Morgan, The Pope, Prince Andrew, Prince Charles, Prince Harry, Prince William, Priti Patel, The Queen, Richard Branson, Rishi Sunak, RuPaul, Taylor Swift, Tiger Woods, Tyson Fury, Vladimir Putin and Xi Jinping, all falling under the show’s legendary gaze.

A next generation of satirical writers and voice artists are working with established talent to drive a new wave of ‘public service satire’.  Writers on the show include: Al Murray, Bert Tyler-Moore & George Jeffrie (The Windsors), Bill Odenkirk (The Simpsons), Brona C. Titley (The Tracey Ullman Show), David X. Cohen (The Simpsons), Gemma Arrowsmith (The Tracey Ullman Show), Jason Hazeley & Nico Tatarowicz (Charlie Brooker’s Screenwipe/Murder in Successville), Karl Minns (Russell Howard’s Good News), Keisha Zollar (Astronomy Club), Laura Major (Famalam), Matt Forde, Patric Verrone (The Simpsons), Phil Wang, Richard Herring, Sophie Duker (Frankie Boyle’s New World Order) and Travis Jay (Dave Chapelle and Friends) with many more joining the growing team.  Voice artists include: Billy West (Futurama), Debra Stephenson (The Impressions Show), Debra Wilson (Family Guy), Guz Khan (Man Like Mobeen), Indira Varma (Game of Thrones), Jess Robinson (The Imitation Game), John DiMaggio (Futurama), Lewis MacLeod (Dead Ringers), Lobo Chan (Killing Eve), Luke Kempner (The Imitation Game), Matt Forde (Unspun) and Phil LaMarr (Pulp Fiction), with many more joining as the puppet cast grows.

snippet.title: The Pengest Munch Ep. 29: Chicken City (Twickenham)
snippet.description:
What's good people? Once again, back in the Nether regions of London. I heard there were deer in Richmond park, and although we saw a couple bait ones on the frontlines, we went deeper into the jungle and there was nothing there, so in the middle of the bush we just did the review and I had to save a spare wing because they were leng. It's kinda jokes how everything that slaps, my brain instinctively is drawn to a 4.6 😂 I'm gonna try consciously veer away from that in future. But yh this place was calm, large up the builders and supporters I saw there. Since it's Black History Month, the next couple episodes are gonna be kinda different. Stay tuned. Safe. 

P.S. For the real ones who  saw this already, I accidentally uploaded a low quality version earlier, but I had to slap up the higher quality one.

Subscribe, Like & Share the ting! Also, tell a friend to turn on their post notifications.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk 2077 — No Limits
snippet.description:
Our second Cyberpunk 2077 commercial starring Keanu Reeves!

Cyberpunk 2077, an open-world, action-adventure story from CD PROJEKT RED, is coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC on November 19th, 2020, with the version for Google Stadia set to launch the same year. The game will also be playable on Xbox Series X and PlayStation 5 consoles when available.

Pre-order now: https://www.cyberpunk.net/pre-order

About the game:
Cyberpunk 2077 is an open-world, action-adventure story set in Night City, a megalopolis obsessed with power, glamour and body modification. You play as V, a mercenary outlaw going after a one-of-a-kind implant that is the key to immortality. You can customize your character’s cyberware, skillset and playstyle, and explore a vast city where the choices you make shape the story and the world around you.

Learn more:
https://www.cyberpunk.net 
https://www.twitter.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.facebook.com/CyberpunkGame 
https://www.instagram.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.discord.gg/CyberpunkGame
https://www.CyberpunkGame.tumblr.com

Music:
Billie Eilish – bad guy
Written by Billie Eilish O'Connell, Finneas O'Connell
(P) 2019 Darkroom/Interscope Records
Licensed by Universal Music Polska
ISRC/ID: USUM71900764

snippet.title: A New Way to Make Custom Pins!!
snippet.description:
Hey guys! Today I have a video for you that kinda started as one thing, but then morphed into something else haha. I thought that i was going to be testing an art/craft kit for this video called "glass stone art craft kit." BUT, I ended up not liking the kit so much and being uninspired by the supplies included. so, i decided to go off on my own creative adventure lol. I used this kit to create a new batch of DIY custom pins. If you've been around my channel for a while you will know that I love making custom pins. I've made them with clay, shrink plastic, and even hot glue. But this was my first time using glass pendants to create pins. I was able to create my own digital art using an app on my ipad called  Procreate to draw some designs for my pins and make them completely custom.
Sorry if this video was kind of all over the place, but I definitely had fun and I really hope you like the final result.


TIME IS RUNNING OUT!
ORDER THE LIMITED GEORGIE PLUSH:  https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/


Here is the kit I'm using (this is an affiliate link):
https://amzn.to/30nd8Fx


___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh 😂 ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 25 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating, painting and general art videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. And even some baking (REALLY bad at that, but it's fun to try LOL). 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Craft Kit Testing: pretty self explanatory. testing craft kits.



___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Every Friday at 4:00pm ET: Alternating Squishy Makeovers, Thrift Makeovers, Craft Kit Reviews, Create This Book, Mail Openings and Miscellaneous crafts and DIYs


____PURCHASE ME PRODUCTS____

CREATE THIS BOOK:
https://amzn.to/2vUerfI

CREATE THIS BOOK 2:
https://amzn.to/2Nx2G9f

ME Custom Merchandise:
https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/

ME Pin & Sticker Shop:
https://me-merch.myshopify.com

ME Printed Apparel and Accessories:
https://moriah-elizabeth.teespring.com/


____ME SOCIALS____

INSTAGRAM: 
https://www.instagram.com/moriahelizabethofficial/

TIKTOK:
https://www.tiktok.com/@me.moriah.elizabeth

VISIT ME WEBSITE:
https://www.moriahelizabeth.com/


____CONTACT ME____

EMAIL PICTURES OF YOUR ART (Create This Book or Fan art only please):
Artwork@Moriah.video

FOR BUSINESS INQUIRIES/OPPORTUNITIES ONLY:
moriah@nightmedia.co


_____MAIL ME_____

For sending squishies, Letters, or general fan mail, please contact: FANMAIL@MORIAH.VIDEO to request my P.O. box address 
(must be 13+ to send mail)
ATTENTION: Unfortunately I can only respond to a small amount of people each week. This is to make sure that I get a reasonable amount of mail and can feature the maximum amount on camera. I apologize in advance if you do not hear back from me, I may not have even seen the message. This email gets SUPER clogged with thousands of messages. Currently have 15,000+ unread messages just in this folder. SORRY PEEPS!*

snippet.title: Michael Ball: Past & Present Tour - FULL SHOW | The Shows Must Go On
snippet.description:
This Friday on The Shows Must Go On we celebrate Michael Ball's legendary career on the West End stage and the full performance of his Past & Present show live from the Royal Albert Hall.

Available for 48 hours Only! Make sure you don't miss out!

Join Michael Ball as he belts show-stopping hits from the musicals including Gethsemane (Jesus Christ Superstar), Empty Chairs At Empty Tables (Les Miserables) and Love Changes Everything (Aspects of Love).

Donate to The Shoot Star Children's Hospice here:
https://www.shootingstar.org.uk/donate/

Donate to The Royal Theatrical Fund here:
https://www.justgiving.com/trtf/Donate

snippet.title: Olive and Mabel - Run With Us
snippet.description: Wasn't going to post but then Olive said that Mabel had her video on the beach. It's not very creative, but again, there are worse things to do with 90 seconds than watch a Labrador's ears. I apologise that Olive didn't clean the lens.

snippet.title: RETURNING TO THE BACKYARD TRAILS FOR MORE BUILDING!! LOCKDOWN EP24
snippet.description: I’m finally back from filming a new Red Bull slopestyle MTB video, and returning to the backyard dirt jumps has been a shock! The weeds are out of control and the jumps have never looked so bad. The project is back on with more features being built, jumps being turned back into smooth trails. And new ideas to ride. Enjoy some fresh build lapses and I’m excited to read your comments now I’m back uploading videos. Legends!

snippet.title: Joe Biden and Donald Trump's fiery first debate—Here are the highlights
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden got heated during their first chance to challenge each other face to face during the first presidential debate. Hardly a minute went by without one of the candidates interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus, the Supreme Court or the economy. Even the moderator, Fox News' Chris Wallace, couldn't always stay above the fray. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden had their first chance to challenge each other face to face. They did — a lot.

Hardly a minute went by in the 90-minute brawl without one of the candidates angrily interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus pandemic, the Supreme Court, the economy or anything else, including each other’s families.

“Will you shut up, man?” Biden snapped at Trump at one point. “You’re the worst president America has ever had,” he said later.

“China ate your lunch,” Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

Even the moderator, Fox News’ Chris Wallace, couldn’t always stay above the fray.

“I hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn’t I be different than the two of you?” the exasperated host said at one point.

Here are the highlights.

snippet.localized.title: Joe Biden and Donald Trump's fiery first debate—Here are the highlights
snippet.localized.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden got heated during their first chance to challenge each other face to face during the first presidential debate. Hardly a minute went by without one of the candidates interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus, the Supreme Court or the economy. Even the moderator, Fox News' Chris Wallace, couldn't always stay above the fray. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden had their first chance to challenge each other face to face. They did — a lot.

Hardly a minute went by in the 90-minute brawl without one of the candidates angrily interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus pandemic, the Supreme Court, the economy or anything else, including each other’s families.

“Will you shut up, man?” Biden snapped at Trump at one point. “You’re the worst president America has ever had,” he said later.

“China ate your lunch,” Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

Even the moderator, Fox News’ Chris Wallace, couldn’t always stay above the fray.

“I hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn’t I be different than the two of you?” the exasperated host said at one point.

Here are the highlights.

snippet.title: 黃鴻升 Alien Huang 柯有倫 Alan Kuo 竇智孔 Bobby Dou 【扛得住 Carry On】Official Music Video
snippet.description:
【ROCK HDMV】
歡迎訂閱滾石唱片YouTube官方頻道 → http://bit.ly/RockRecords
#黃鴻升 #柯有倫 #竇智孔  《#扛得住》MV

Alien留給地球的最後一首友情歌
願大家一起將正能量傳出去

Alien黃鴻升「Plan B 專輯」第5首單曲
《扛得住》
黃鴻升 X 柯有倫 X 竇智孔
三位好友合唱
為後疫情時代的我們加油打氣
兄弟陪你一定可以扛得住

ALIEN黃鴻升2020專輯「Plan B」，從2019年開始籌備製作，這張專輯從最開始的A&R到專輯概念、企劃文案、拍攝ＭＶ，黃鴻升不假手他人，全部自己一手包辦，經紀人曾經擔心他手上工作太多太忙，在他寫歌詞卡關的時候，跟他說要不要乾脆找人寫詞，他思考了幾秒，肯定地說，他可以的，他自己來！

2019年6月陸續推出《蒸發》、《人生定番》、《Plan B》，時隔多月，在2020年6月再推出《我不是空笑夢》，在忙碌於主持節目、廣告代言、戲劇之外，黃鴻升對於歌手身份，已不想要只是做一個被公司規劃好的「歌手」，而是希望透過自己親手創作歌詞、寫歌曲介紹文案、拍攝ＭＶ，為自己的音樂找定位，為自己想唱的歌創造生命。

這首《扛得住》，預定在2020年9月底上架，在9月13日釋出歌名與三人的宣傳照，只是，來不及讓大家讀到他為這首歌寫的介紹文字。
所以，延續「Plan B」的精神，催生這首歌的柯有倫，以及共同合唱的竇智孔，各自為好友黃鴻升、為三人合唱的這首歌，寫下一段話，希望能夠真切傳達，關於這首歌的誕生、靈感與精神。

Alan柯有倫：
這首歌的誕生，最大的原因，其實是因爲今年疫情的關係，看到大家生活上面都遇到一些比較大的困苦，所以想要鼓勵大家，在這段時間一定要扛得住。

我們有個高爾夫球群組，前一陣子三個人常一起去高爾夫球練習場練球，因爲我們三個都希望，從今年開始，即使再忙，我們三個人都可以保持每一個月一定要下場打一場高爾夫球。
有一天，因爲這首歌寫出來，我就傳到群組裡面給他們聽，我說有沒有機會跟兩位兄弟一起唱這首歌。當然，他們兩個一聽完之後，立刻答應。
後來，我們去錄音室錄完這首歌的時候，鴻升跟我說，他希望可以把這首歌放在他的全新專輯，我跟竇哥聽了之後，當然也是一口答應。

這首歌詞曲創作的靈感，就像當年的《笨小孩》，我一直希望可以做一首是像當年的笨小孩，有三個兄弟，用一首曲子表達一種正面的力量。
我們三個人的想法應該都是一樣的，就是希望在生命裏面很簡單，然後可以做一件事情，是讓我們三個人都覺得是很正面，然後很快樂的。
在這個打拼的路上，我們三個兄弟互相都看到彼此的辛苦，也看到彼此的堅持與執着。希望能用這種心境，去鼓勵所有不管是遇到困難、或者是遇到挫折的人。

想跟鴻升說的就是，這一趟太短了，下輩子我們再做朋友、我們再做兄弟，有你在身邊一起並肩作戰，是我這一輩子最驕傲最光榮的事。

竇智孔：
9月18日.晚上18:42分
在收到滾石發來的信息後，
我想這是你搞的鬼吧！
我崩潰了。
你..太賤了....
我會在我的隱形筆記本裡註記的。
然後，
我回頭翻著簡訊，
我找到了我們兄弟情開始的地方。
我承認我不是一個好相處的人。
但你的舉動讓我決定把牆全打開了。
簡訊裡
我：我們外景提來賓，不知道你會不會願意來幫忙。
你：只要你需要我的，我就盡全力幫忙，ok!（你就是這麼可愛）
我想緣分就是這麼簡單
然後，我們完成了一些回憶，
當然我們還有很多約好的計畫……

沒事，兄弟，再見。
兄弟我扛得住！
我們保持聯絡⋯。

⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯

『無論是逼不得已，或是因為是退卻而放棄、
無論如何，儘管緊緊擁抱遺憾，時間仍舊不可逆。
時針分針秒針，前進的頻率不同， 方向卻總是一致。
時針不會為了你而開始逆轉，但你可以順著時間的流，釐清造成的不甘的源頭，
毫無懸念的繼續順時針前行。』

—截自Alien黃鴻升，2019/11/28 寫於「Plan B」專輯概念

計劃趕不上變化、時間也無法倒轉，
面對遺憾和困難，請讓 扛得住 成為定番。

這是他留給地球的最後一首友情歌，只要有音樂陪伴，相信大家一定扛得住；願每個人都永遠記得鴻升帶來的美好，一起將他的正能量傳遞出去。

黃鴻升 柯有倫 竇智孔《扛得住》♫ https://RockRecordsCo.lnk.to/CarryOn

時針不會為了你而開始逆轉，但你可以順著時間的流，釐清造成的不甘的源頭，
毫無懸念的繼續順時針前行。』

—截自Alien黃鴻升，2019/11/28 寫於「Plan B」專輯概念

計劃趕不上變化、時間也無法倒轉，
面對遺憾和困難，請讓 扛得住 成為定番。

這是他留給地球的最後一首友情歌，只要有音樂陪伴，相信大家一定扛得住；願每個人都永遠記得鴻升帶來的美好，一起將他的正能量傳遞出去。

国庆特别节目坚持深入生活、扎根人民的发展思想，设立“风雨同舟，激荡爱国情怀”、“疫情防控，坚定制度自信”、“开放包容，彰显大国担当”、 “团结奋斗，决战脱贫攻坚”、“携手同行，奔向幸福小康”、“不忘初心，喜迎建党百年 ”6大主题内容，通过歌舞、杂技、沉浸式讲述等丰富多彩的节目形式致敬抗疫、抗洪英雄，展现脱贫攻坚的伟大成果，传承家国情怀，弘扬中国精神，进一步激励全民，鼓舞人心。

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Liverpool vs Arsenal (3-1) | Premier League
snippet.description:
Our winning start to the season is over after Liverpool fought back to beat us at Anfield.
 
A bizarre goal from Alex Lacazette saw us lead the champions and lay the foundations for a memorable result. But our advantage lasted just two minutes as Sadio Mane and Andy Robertson struck to turn the tide in Liverpool's favour.

Diogo Jota then put the game to bed moments before full time with a crisp finish into the bottom left-hand corner. 

#arsenal #highlights #premierleague

snippet.title: First US Presidential debate: the 'highlights'
snippet.description:
Highlights (if you can call them that) from the first US Presidential debate between Donald Trump and Joe Biden in Ohio. 

The two men frequently interrupted each other with angry interjections, with Mr Biden eventually snapping at his opponent: "Will you shut up, man?"

snippet.title: President Trump and Melania Trump test positive for Covid-19
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump tested positive for coronavirus, the President announced early Friday morning, an extraordinary development coming months into a global pandemic and in the final stretch of his reelection campaign.
"Tonight, @FLOTUS and I tested positive for COVID-19. We will begin our quarantine and recovery process immediately. We will get through this TOGETHER!" Trump tweeted shortly before 1 am Friday.
In a memo issued to reporters around 1 a.m. ET, the President's physician, Navy Commander Dr. Sean Conley, wrote he received confirmation of the positive tests on Thursday evening.
"The President and First Lady are both well at this time, and they plan to remain at home within the White House during their convalescence," Conley wrote.

#Covid #Trump #CNN #News

snippet.title: Joe Biden and President Donald Trump spar in first debate: 'Will you shut up, man?'
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden face off in the first presidential debate Tuesday night, hosted by Case Western Reserve University in Cleveland, Ohio. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden had their first chance to challenge each other face to face. They did — a lot.

Hardly a minute went by in the 90-minute brawl without one of the candidates angrily interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus pandemic, the Supreme Court, the economy or anything else, including each other’s families.

“Will you shut up, man?” Biden snapped at Trump at one point. “You’re the worst president America has ever had,” he said later.

“China ate your lunch,” Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

Even the moderator, Fox News’ Chris Wallace, couldn’t always stay above the fray.

“I hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn’t I be different than the two of you?” the exasperated host said at one point.

snippet.title: Joe Biden and President Donald Trump discuss Covid-19 in first debate
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden face off in the first presidential debate Tuesday night, hosted by Case Western Reserve University in Cleveland, Ohio. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

Biden swiped at Trump over the president’s early handling of the coronavirus, alleging that the administration started to inform the public of the disease’s severity only when it hit the stock market.

“Do you believe for a moment what he’s telling you in light of all the lies he’s told you about the whole issue relating to Covid?” Biden asked. “He still hasn’t even acknowledged that he knew this was happening — knew how dangerous it would be back in February — and he didn’t even tell you.”

“He panicked, or just looked at the stock market, one of the two,” Biden added. “Because guess what? A lot of people died and a lot more are going to die unless he gets a lot smarter or a lot quicker.”

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden face off in the first presidential debate Tuesday night, hosted by Case Western Reserve University in Cleveland, Ohio. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

Biden swiped at Trump over the president’s early handling of the coronavirus, alleging that the administration started to inform the public of the disease’s severity only when it hit the stock market.

“Do you believe for a moment what he’s telling you in light of all the lies he’s told you about the whole issue relating to Covid?” Biden asked. “He still hasn’t even acknowledged that he knew this was happening — knew how dangerous it would be back in February — and he didn’t even tell you.”

“He panicked, or just looked at the stock market, one of the two,” Biden added. “Because guess what? A lot of people died and a lot more are going to die unless he gets a lot smarter or a lot quicker.”

snippet.title: BTS: Tiny Desk (Home) Concert
snippet.description:
For new music, the latest Tiny Desk (home) concerts and more, sign up for the NPR Music newsletter, sent weekly: npr.org/nprmusicnewsletter

Sept. 21, 2020 | Stephen Thompson -- We've been trying to make a BTS Tiny Desk concert happen for years now — even gaming out ways we might move Bob Boilen's desk far enough forward to accommodate the superstar Korean boy band's dance moves.

In the end, it took a global pandemic — and the launch of Tiny Desk (home) concerts back in March — to make something happen. With BTS cooped up in Seoul, the group held true to the series's spirit by convening a live band for its Tiny Desk debut, and even arranged to perform in a workspace with a music-friendly backdrop: the record store VINYL & PLASTIC by Hyundai Card in BTS's hometown.

Opening with this summer's inescapable "Dynamite" — the group's first single to hit No. 1 in the U.S., as well as its first song to be fully recorded in English — BTS leaned hard into the new track's celebratory, "Uptown Funk"-adjacent vibes. From there, the group dipped into its back catalog, seizing on the opportunity to showcase its quieter side while (mostly) staying uncharacteristically seated. The breezily propulsive "Save ME," from 2016, ultimately gave way to a full-on power ballad in 2017's reflective "Spring Day."

The latter track seemed especially true to BTS's hopeful nature: Introduced with a few optimistic words from rapper and singer RM ("It's been the roughest summer ever, but we know that spring will come"), the song reflects on a need to wait out hard times, even as the weight of present-day pain feels oppressive.

BTS had intended to spend 2020 delighting the BTS Army in arenas around the world, only to spend these last few months performing in isolation. Released on the last day of a grim season, "Spring Day" provides a nice reminder of what awaits us on the other side. We just have to get through fall and winter first.

SET LIST
"Dynamite"
"Save ME"
"Spring Day"

MUSICIANS
V: vocals; Jin: vocals; Jimin: vocals; J-Hope: vocals; RM: vocals; SUGA: vocals; Jungkook: vocals; KHAN: drums; DOCSKIM: keyboard; Kim Kiwook: bass; Shyun: guitar

CREDITS
Video and Audio by: Big Hit Entertainment; Producer: Stephen Thompson; Audio Mastering Engineer: Josh Rogosin; Video Producer: Morgan Noelle Smith; Associate Producer: Bobby Carter; Executive Producer: Lauren Onkey; Senior VP, Programming: Anya Grundmann


ABOUT THE SERIES

The Tiny Desk is working from home for the foreseeable future. Introducing NPR Music's Tiny Desk (home) concerts, bringing you performances from across the country and the world. It's the same spirit — stripped-down sets, an intimate setting — just a different space.

snippet.title: Sen Çal Kapımı 12. Bölüm
snippet.description:
Serkan sonunda aşkını itiraf etti. Sıra Eda’da. Ama bu kadar olaydan sonra kolay olmayacak Eda’nın itirafını almak. Serkan sabırla bekliyor Eda’nın aşık olduğunu duymak için. Bir de ailelerden saklama meselesi var. Eda nişan sözleşmesini öğrenen halasına Serkan’la sevgili olduğunu söyleyemiyor. Eda’nın ısrarıyla Serkan da kabul ediyor kimseye söylememeyi. Serkan ve Eda ilişkilerini gizli tutarken birçok macera yaşayacaklar. 

Sen Çal Kapımı Ailesine Katılmak için: https://bit.ly/3jB1Rsj﻿
Sen Çal Kapımı Resmi Youtube Kanalı: https://bit.ly/3dxNPVW

Hande Erçel ve Kerem Bürsin’ e; dizide Neslihan Yeldan, Bige Önal, Evrim Doğan, İsmail Ege Şaşmaz, Anıl İlter, Melisa Döngel, Çağrı Çıtanak, Elçin Afacan, Sitare Akbaş, Başak Gümülcinelioğlu, Alican Aytekin, Sarp Bozkurt, İlkyaz Arslan ve Ahmet Somers gibi birbirinden başarılı isimler eşlik edecek.

snippet.title: Joe Biden and Donald Trump's fiery first debate—Here are the highlights
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden got heated during their first chance to challenge each other face to face during the first presidential debate. Hardly a minute went by without one of the candidates interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus, the Supreme Court or the economy. Even the moderator, Fox News' Chris Wallace, couldn't always stay above the fray. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden had their first chance to challenge each other face to face. They did — a lot.

Hardly a minute went by in the 90-minute brawl without one of the candidates angrily interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus pandemic, the Supreme Court, the economy or anything else, including each other’s families.

“Will you shut up, man?” Biden snapped at Trump at one point. “You’re the worst president America has ever had,” he said later.

“China ate your lunch,” Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

Even the moderator, Fox News’ Chris Wallace, couldn’t always stay above the fray.

“I hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn’t I be different than the two of you?” the exasperated host said at one point.

Here are the highlights.

snippet.title: President Trump and Melania Trump test positive for Covid-19
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump tested positive for coronavirus, the President announced early Friday morning, an extraordinary development coming months into a global pandemic and in the final stretch of his reelection campaign.
"Tonight, @FLOTUS and I tested positive for COVID-19. We will begin our quarantine and recovery process immediately. We will get through this TOGETHER!" Trump tweeted shortly before 1 am Friday.
In a memo issued to reporters around 1 a.m. ET, the President's physician, Navy Commander Dr. Sean Conley, wrote he received confirmation of the positive tests on Thursday evening.
"The President and First Lady are both well at this time, and they plan to remain at home within the White House during their convalescence," Conley wrote.

#Covid #Trump #CNN #News

snippet.title: Israel Adesanya addresses pectoral controversy, Jon Jones trash talk at UFC 253 | ESPN MMA
snippet.description:
Israel Adesanya returns to Ariel Helwani’s MMA Show to look back at his TKO win over Paulo Costa at UFC 253 to defend his middleweight title. Adesanya (3:19) reacts to the talk on social media about his right pectoral and Jon Jones’ comments (7:05) after the fight. “The Last Stylebender” also teases that he has a few things in the works regarding his (20:06) next fight, which he hopes will be in 2020.

snippet.title: President Trump and First Lady test positive for COVID-19
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and First Lady Melania have tested positive for coronavirus.

The 74-year-old said the couple were self-isolating after Hope Hicks, one of his top aides, tested positive.

His health records showed he is categorised as obese, putting him at higher risk of serious complications from the virus.

snippet.title: Jacinda Ardern admits cannabis use in heated New Zealand debate
snippet.description:
New Zealand's prime minister, Jacinda Ardern, has admitted to using cannabis 'a long time ago', in a heated televised debate with the opposition leader, Judith Collins.

Speaking during the 90-minute debate on Newshub, the Labour leader and incumbent PM chose not to disclose how she would vote in the forthcoming cannabis referendum, drawing ire from her opponent, the National party leader

snippet.title: Trump and Biden face off in chaotic first 2020 presidential debate | FULL DEBATE
snippet.description:
The first presidential debate between President Trump and Joe Biden featured a chaotic series of bitter exchanges and name-calling, with the president repeatedly speaking over his Democratic rival and the moderator struggling to maintain control of the 90-minute affair.

"Will you shut up, man?" an exasperated Biden said in a comment that was emblematic of the tumultuous nature of the debate, which was held in Cleveland, Ohio. "It's hard to get any word in with this clown."

The president leveled barrages of unfounded accusations against his Democratic rival and his family, invoking his son Hunter Biden's work in Ukraine and bringing up the younger Biden's history of drug abuse. Mr. Trump declined to condemn white supremacist groups and defended his response to the coronavirus pandemic that has claimed more than 200,000 American lives, trying to portray Biden as a socialist who isn't equipped to occupy the Oval Office.

"Did you use the word smart?" the president asked Biden at one point. "You graduated either the lowest or almost the lowest in your class. Don't ever use the word smart with me, Joe."

Biden, for his part, tried to direct his answers to the audience watching at home. He called Mr. Trump "the worst president America has ever had," blaming him for bungling the response to the pandemic and fueling racial divisions amid recent protests against police brutality.

"Will you shut up, man?" an exasperated Biden said in a comment that was emblematic of the tumultuous nature of the debate, which was held in Cleveland, Ohio. "It's hard to get any word in with this clown."

The president leveled barrages of unfounded accusations against his Democratic rival and his family, invoking his son Hunter Biden's work in Ukraine and bringing up the younger Biden's history of drug abuse. Mr. Trump declined to condemn white supremacist groups and defended his response to the coronavirus pandemic that has claimed more than 200,000 American lives, trying to portray Biden as a socialist who isn't equipped to occupy the Oval Office.

"Did you use the word smart?" the president asked Biden at one point. "You graduated either the lowest or almost the lowest in your class. Don't ever use the word smart with me, Joe."

Biden, for his part, tried to direct his answers to the audience watching at home. He called Mr. Trump "the worst president America has ever had," blaming him for bungling the response to the pandemic and fueling racial divisions amid recent protests against police brutality.

#PresidentialDebate #2020Election #2020Debates #DonaldTrump #JoeBiden

snippet.title: Lagum - NINGUÉM ME ENSINOU
snippet.description:
Vídeo Oficial de "Ninguem Me Ensinou" de Lagum.

Ouça agora: https://lagum.lnk.to/NinguemMeEnsinou

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Em memória do nosso baterista, Tio Wilson.

Foram 4 anos com o Tio na nossa batera. Juntos, produzimos e lançamos 25 músicas, e antes de partir ele deixou muita coisa gravada. Dessas, “NINGUÉM ME ENSINOU” era a sua preferida. E se tem algo que o Tio nos ensinou é a importância de agradecer e reconhecer quem fortalece o nosso sonho. Então essa música é dedicada a todos os fãs, amigos e familiares do Tio, que de alguma forma contribuíram pra isso tudo se realizar.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

"Ninguém me ensinou"
(Lagum)

A vida é boa pacarai,
nem sei por que eu tô chorando
Eu tenho vinte e poucos anos
e não vou parar aqui

Eu sinto falta da minha casa,
minha mãe sente minha falta
Tudo bem, essa é a vida que eu escolhi

Desde pequeno falam que eu sou curioso
Quem me viu quem me vê,
fala que eu nunca cresci

Não tenho medo de errar,
só medo de desistir
Mas tenho vinte e poucos
e não vou parar aqui

Quem te ensinou a sonhar?
Quem te ensinou a sonhar?
(2x)

Mas se garotos não choram alguém diz o que eu sou?
Nanananão, fica calado.
Eu sou o que eu quiser
Eu sou o sol da meia noite e a lua cheia de manhã
Mas me visto de mim mesmo da cabeça aos pés

Eu tenho vinte e tantos planos pra antes dos 30 anos
Alguém diz pra onde vamos,
tenho pressa de existir

Me disseram, calma mano,
“cê” tem tempo sobrando
Pra errar, e eu to certo que não vou parar aqui

Quem te ensinou a sonhar?
Quem te ensinou a sonhar?
(2x) 

Ôôô ninguém me ensinou
pra onde eu vou, ninguém vai
Ôôô ninguém me ensinou
pra onde eu vou, ninguém vai

Quem te ensinou a sonhar?
Quem te ensinou a sonhar?

snippet.title: Experimente o futuro com pagamento por aproximação | Conteúdo Acessível - Libras
snippet.description:
Os tempos mudaram e a rotina já não é a mesma. Nem mesmo para a família do futuro. Com as inovações do Bradesco, Os Jetsons contam com várias facilidades. 
Como quando Astor come a carteira de George, por exemplo.
Ainda bem que George já vive no futuro e pode usar pagamento por aproximação, sem precisar da carteira. 
Pros desafios do presente, experimente o futuro com o Bradesco.

#PraCegoVer: O filme começa com o lettering “Bradesco apresenta: Os Jetsons”. George está em um pet shop e segura várias sacolas em direção ao caixa. Um robô passa as compras pela esteira. George procura a carteira nos bolsos. Ao olhar para o lado, o cão Astor comeu a carteira e ela fica destruída. George se lembra que tem um smartwatch e paga as compras por aproximação. George e Astor saem do pet shop segurando sacolas de compras. Vemos a frase “pros desafios do presente, experimente o futuro com o Bradesco”. Ao lado da frase, há uma nave com o holograma do logo do Bradesco.


Interpretação em Libras: Carlos Di Oliveira
Edição e finalização: PH Soluções Audiovisuais

#Jetsons #ExperimenteOFuturo
